{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Demonstrações de tecnologia web aberta","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/Demos","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p class=\"summary\">A mozilla suporta uma grande variedade de tecnologias abertas da web aberta e nós encorajamos seu uso.Esta página oferece links para demonstrações interessantes dessas tecnologia.</p>\n\n<p>Se você conhece uma boa demonstração ou aplicação da tecnologia web aberta, adicione um link para a seção apropriada aqui.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gráficos_2d","title":"Gráficos 2D","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"tela_de_pintura","title":"Tela de pintura","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"http://www.blobsallad.se/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Blob Sallad: an interactive blob using javascript and canvas</a> (<a href=\"http://blobsallad.se/article/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">code demos)</a></p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"http://arapehlivanian.com/wp-content/uploads/2007/02/canvas.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Flying through space</a></p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"http://mdn.github.io/canvas-raycaster/index.html\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/editor/fckeditor/core/editor/samples/raycaster/RayCaster.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">3D RayCaster</a></p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"https://processingjs.org/exhibition/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">processing.js</a></p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"http://gyu.que.jp/jscloth/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">3D&nbsp;on 2D&nbsp;Canvas</a></p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"http://viliusle.github.io/miniPaint/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">miniPaint: Image editor</a> (<a href=\"https://github.com/viliusle/miniPaint\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">source code</a>)</p>\n </li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"svg","title":"SVG","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"http://starkravingfinkle.org/projects/demo/svg-bubblemenu-in-html.xml\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bubblemenu</a> (visual effects and interaction)</p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"http://starkravingfinkle.org/blog/2007/07/firefox-3-svg-foreignobject/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML transformations</a> using <code>foreignObject</code> (visual effects and transforms)</p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"http://svg-whiz.com/svg/linguistics/theCreepyMouth.svg\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Phonetics Guide</a> (interactive)</p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"http://www.lutanho.net/svgvml3d/platonic.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">3D objects demo</a> (interactive)</p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"https://www.themaninblue.com/experiment/Blobular/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Blobular</a> (interactive)</p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"http://www.double.co.nz/video_test/video.svg\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Video embedded in SVG</a> (or use the <a href=\"http://www.double.co.nz/video_test/video_svg.tar.bz2\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">local download</a>)</p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"http://summerstyle.github.io/summer/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Summer HTML image map creator</a> (<a href=\"https://github.com/summerstyle/summer\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">source code</a>)</p>\n </li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"vídeo","title":"Vídeo","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"https://vimeo.com/172328210\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Video 3D Animation \"mozilla constantly evolving\"</a></p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"https://vimeo.com/173851395\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Video 3D animation \"Floating Dance\"</a></p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"http://www.double.co.nz/video_test/test1.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Streaming Anime, Movie Trailer and Interview</a></p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"http://www.double.co.nz/video_test/test2.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Billy's Browser Firefox Flick</a></p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"http://www.double.co.nz/video_test/test3.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Virtual Barber Shop</a></p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"http://www.double.co.nz/video_test/test4.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Transformers Movie Trailer</a></p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"http://www.double.co.nz/video_test/test5.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">A Scanner Darkly Movie Trailer</a> (with built in controls)</p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"http://www.double.co.nz/video_test/events.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Events firing and volume control</a></p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"http://www.double.co.nz/video_test/video.svg\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Dragable and sizable videos</a></p>\n </li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gráficos_3d","title":"Gráficos 3D","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"webgl","title":"WebGL","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"http://ondras.github.io/fireworks-webgl/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Audio Fireworks</a></p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p>IoQuake3 (<a href=\"https://github.com/klaussilveira/ioquake3.js\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">source code</a>)</p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p>Escher puzzle (<a href=\"https://github.com/micahbolen/demoscene\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">source code</a>)</p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p><a href=\"http://collinhover.github.io/kaiopua/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Kai 'Opua</a> (<a href=\"https://github.com/collinhover/kaiopua\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">source code</a>)</p>\n </li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"realidade_virtual","title":"Realidade virtual","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>\n  <